about.summary: More future! Make Python 2/3 compatibility a bit easier

name: mo-future
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "mo-future" %}
{% set version = "3.17.19324" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 2e13eb6b3fdfe7a772b0a75e0cf9e4e5aa43c4c35ded8db03d8708fbacde96fb

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - mo_future

about:
  home: "https://github.com/klahnakoski/mo-files"
  license: MPL-2.0
  license_family: "MOZILLA"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "More future! Make Python 2/3 compatibility a bit easier"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - xhochy
